                    'More islands appear',
                    'More electricity for us to use',
                    'Animal extinction and island disappearing'

                ],
                'correctIndex': 4,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! Global warming will cause animal extinction due to environmental change. It will also cause the island disappearing due to rising sea level!',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. Global warming will cause animal extinction due to environmental change. It will also cause islands disappearing due to rising sea level!'
            },
            {
                'q': 'When you leave a room, what should you do?',
                'options': [
                    'Do nothing',
                    'Tidy up your bed',
                    'Turn off the lights only',
                    'Turn off all the electrical appliances in the room'
                ],
                'correctIndex': 3,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! You should turn off all the electrical appliances in the room, not just the lights!',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. You should turn off all the electrical appliances in the room, not just the lights!'
            },
            {
                'q': 'What causes Global Warming?',
                'options': [
                    'Reading books',
                    'Using too much electricity',
                    'Playing too much piano',
                    'Playing too much basketball'
                ],
                'correctIndex': 1,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! The major cause of global warming is using too much electricity. Always try to do more fun activities that don’t consume electricity!',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. The major cause of global warming is using too much electricity. Doing fun activities that don’t consume electricity will not cause global warming.'
            },
            {
                'q': 'You see the hair dryer is plugged in and no one is using it. What should you do?',
                'options': [
                    'Unplug it',
                    'Play with it like a gun',
                    'Put it in a refrigerator'
                ],
                'correctIndex': 0,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! Hair dryer is one of the most power-hungry products at home. Be sure to unplug it even if the power is not on!',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. You should unplug the hair dryer even the power is not on! It is one of the most power-hungry products at home.'
            },
            {
                'q': 'Why should we unplug the table lamps when no one is using it?',
                'options': [
                    'It still costs electricity even when power is not on.',
                    'It looks more tidy',               
                    'Just for fun'
                ],
                'correctIndex': 0,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! If you are able to unplug an electrical appliance, then do it! They still cost electricity even when power is not on.',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. If you are able to unplug an electrical appliance, then do it! They still cost electricity even when power is not on.'
            },
            {
                'q': 'You should open the refrigerator door only when you want to...',
                'options': [
                    'Get your food or drink real quick ',
                    'Play with the refrigerator light',
                    'Feel the cool from refrigerator',
                    'Play with the refrigerator door'
                ],
                'correctIndex':0,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! Avoid unnecessarily opening the refrigerator because cold air escapes whenever you open it. It needs to spend electricity to bring the temperature down!',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. You should avoid unnecessarily opening the refrigerator because cold air escapes whenever you open it. It needs to spend electricity to bring the temperature down!'
            }

            ,
            {
                'q': 'Why is taking showers better than baths?',
                'options': [
                    'You can sing in the showers',
                    'Baths are for adults',
                    'Showers use less hot water'
                ],
                'correctIndex': 2,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! Hot water is expensive. Shower is better because it uses less electricity to heat up the water.',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. Hot water is expensive. Shower is better because it uses less electricity to heat up the water.'
            },
            {
                'q': 'It is daylight outside and you feel too dark inside, what should you do?',
                'options': [
                    'Use the light from TV',
                    'Open the curtain to bring in the natural light',
                    'Open all the ceiling lights',
                    'Use a torch light'

                ],
                'correctIndex': 1,
                'correctResponse': 'CORRECT! Draw up the curtain to bring in the natural light. You won’t even need to switch on lights till sunset comes around!',
                'incorrectResponse': 'Incorrect. Draw up the curtain to bring in the natural light. You won’t even need to switch on lights till sunset comes around!'
